Description:
...

Usage: createInstGroup [-help] <group name> [<box>]
                       [-isPhyHier] [-guide <box> | -region | -fence | -softGuide ] [[-ar <num>] -density <num>] [ -softGuide ] [-floating | -softGuide ] [-floating | -guide <box>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<group name>            # name of instance group (string, required)
<box>                   # box in <llx> <lly> <urx> <ury> (box, optional)
-ar <num>               # aspect ratio (float, optional)
-density <num>          # initial desity (float, optional, min=0, max=1)
-fence                  # create fence (bool, optional)
-floating               # Create floating inst group. (bool, optional)
-guide <box>            # create guide with box (box, optional)
-isPhyHier              # create it as a physical hierarchy (bool, optional)
-region                 # create region (bool, optional)
-softGuide              # create softGuide (bool, optional)